I have completed the analysis of `sub_layer_0_01_ai_system` and written the result to the designated result file.

**Summary of findings:**
- **41 files** across 5 directories (root, AATest, Compressor, README_support_docs, tests)
- **AALang** is the first programming language designed to run entirely within LLMs, using JSON-LD graph format
- **GAB** (Generic AALang Builder) is an intelligent agent compiler with a 4-mode workflow
- The system uses an **n-mode-m-actor** architecture pattern with three communication layers
- It integrates with MCP (Model Context Protocol) and A2A (Agent to Agent) protocols
- This is the **primary AI system** used throughout the entire layer-stage framework
